---
import ServiceLayout from '@layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
---

<ServiceLayout
  title="Scented Candle Making Experience"
  description="Blend your own signature scents and create custom scented candles in Centerville, TN. Premium fragrance oils and expert guidance included."
  price="$25-35 per person"
  duration="2 hours"
  location="Centerville, TN"
  keywords="scented candle making, fragrance blending, custom candles, Centerville"
>
  <section slot="overview">
    <h2>Scented Candle Making Experience - Centerville, TN</h2>
    <p>
      Create your own custom-scented candles in our immersive Scented Candle Making Experience. Learn fragrance blending techniques while crafting beautiful candles with unique scent combinations that reflect your personality and preferences.
    </p>

    <h3>The Experience</h3>
    <p>
      This experience focuses on the art of fragrance. You'll work with premium fragrance oils from our extensive collection, learning how different scents complement each other. Our experts guide you in creating unique fragrance blends, then you'll pour your custom-scented candles into beautiful containers.
    </p>

    <h3>What's Included</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Access to 40+ premium fragrance oils</li>
      <li>Fragrance blending guidance from experts</li>
      <li>Premium soy wax and containers</li>
      <li>Professional pouring instruction</li>
      <li>All supplies and materials</li>
      <li>Take home 2-3 custom-scented candles</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Perfect For</h3>
    <p>
      Anyone who loves scents and wants to create personalized candles. Perfect for aromatherapy enthusiasts, gift-makers, and those seeking a unique creative experience.
    </p>

    <h3>Fragrance Profiles Available</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Floral & Fresh (lavender, rose, honeysuckle)</li>
      <li>Fruity & Sweet (apple, peach, vanilla)</li>
      <li>Woody & Warm (cedarwood, sandalwood, amber)</li>
      <li>Spicy & Exotic (cinnamon, clove, patchouli)</li>
      <li>Herbal & Natural (eucalyptus, mint, sage)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How It Works</h3>
    <ol>
      <li>Welcome and fragrance education (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Explore fragrance options and take notes (15 minutes)</li>
      <li>Blend your custom fragrances (20 minutes)</li>
      <li>Pour your custom-scented candles (30 minutes)</li>
      <li>Finishing touches (10 minutes)</li>
    </ol>

    <h3>Pricing & Duration</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Price:</strong> $25-35 per person<br />
      <strong>Duration:</strong> 2 hours<br />
      <strong>Group Size:</strong> 1-6 people<br />
      <strong>Skill Level:</strong> All levels welcome
    </p>

    <div style="background: #e8f4f8; padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin: 2rem 0; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><strong>Book your scent experience!</strong> Call (931) 729-8459 or email made@thelocalplacetn.com. Located at 111 South Public Square, Upstairs, Centerville, TN 37033.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="testimonials">
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"I loved creating my own fragrance blend! The staff knew so much about scents. My custom candles smell amazing!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Grace P.</strong> - Nashville (45 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"Perfect gift-making activity! I created custom candles for everyone on my list. They were such a hit!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Rachel H.</strong> - Brentwood (40 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--cream); padding: 1.5rem; border-left: 4px solid var(--brown); margin-bottom: 1.5rem; border-radius: 4px;">
      <p><em>"The fragrance blending was my favorite part. I now have signature scents I can't find anywhere else!"</em></p>
      <p><strong>Emma S.</strong> - Franklin (35 minutes away)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section slot="related">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem;">
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Custom Scent Candle Creation</h3>
        <p>Design your own unique fragrance blend for a personalized candle.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/custom-scent-candle-creation" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Essential Oil Candle Workshop</h3>
        <p>Create luxurious candles using pure essential oils.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/essential-oil-candle-workshop" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--light-gray); padding: 1.5rem; border-radius: 8px;">
        <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Pour Your Own Candle Class</h3>
        <p>Create beautiful hand-poured candles with custom colors and scents.</p>
        <a href="/candle-store/pour-your-own-candle-class" style="color: var(--brown); text-decoration: underline;">Learn More →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</ServiceLayout>
